    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in legendary Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the high-revving S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically, the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been preemptively reinforced with precision plates. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, providing exceptional torque vectoring. Every bushing is factory-spec, ensuring the chassis maintains its original torsional rigidity. No fluid leaks, no dash lights, and a pristine interior that retains its factory Alcantara texture. This is a collector-grade driver\u2019s machine for the discerning purist.",
