      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and is basically flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s as close to new as it gets without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Come take a look!",
